data.description: EXCITING NEWS! Your dream home just became even more irresistible! With a  $20K PRICE REDUCTION and $5K TORWARDS BUYERS CLOSING COSTS, this stunning two-story Trillium gem is calling your name! this stunning two-story Trillium gem is calling your name! Welcome to your new family haven nestled in the desirable Trillium neighborhood! This stunning two-story home is ready to embrace your family with its 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, and a 2-car garage. The ground floor opens up to versatile living spaces, perfect for both relaxed family time and lively gatherings. The kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting a breakfast bar, a cozy dining nook, shiny stainless steel appliances, and charming wooden cabinets.  Upstairs, a sanctuary of bedrooms awaits you. The lavish master suite spoils you with a walk-in closet and a bathroom featuring double sinks, a relaxing garden tub, and a spacious shower. Step outside to your personal oasis – a covered back patio, the ideal spot for firing up the grill or simply kicking back with your favorite drink while soaking in that wonderful Florida sunshine.  Trillium is not just a neighborhood; it's a community offering fantastic amenities such as a clubhouse, a cool pool, and a playful playground. With the Suncoast Parkway nearby, reaching Tampa is a breeze, and you're also within easy reach of fantastic shopping and dining options. Don't just imagine it, live it – schedule your appointment today to experience the magic of this home for yourself!
